rows.label: qst201811_msg0001
rows.name:
What? You want to know
my favorite food?

rows.label: qst201811_msg0002
rows.name:
The most delicious thing around
here is the Trippy Catfish.

rows.label: qst201811_msg0003
rows.name:
It's fascinating to watch them
swim, and they're delicious to
eat. Isn't that the best?

rows.label: qst201811_msg0004
rows.name:
All the Phonexes in
Temperantia love to eat them.

rows.label: qst201811_msg0005
rows.name:
Pepe-chan? I haven't
seen anyone like that.

rows.label: qst201811_msg0006
rows.name:
We have a settlement in the
Holy Grail's Hammer, so you
might want to ask there.
